{"type":"message","id":"f6870245","parentId":"b718bc60","timestamp":"2026-06-25T06:04:19.519Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**有用！** opencli 是个**网站 CLI 转换器**——它能直接给 148 个网站（包括 tiktok、taobao、jd、xiaohongshu 等）生成命令化操作接口。\n\n但**等一下**——我得先确认一件事：site list 里没看到 `tiktok-shop`，只有 `tiktok`（普通版）。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_vbzelk5s3hde_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"opencli tiktok --help 2>&1 | head -40\necho \"===\"\nopencli list 2>&1 | grep -iE \"tiktok|seller|shopee|amazon\" | head -20"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":2522,"output":147,"cacheRead":78194,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":80863,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782367453099,"responseId":"068bf7ddcf902452b4b9076292777dc0","responseModel":"MiniMax-M3"}}
{"type":"message","id":"d7d35a21","parentId":"f6870245","timestamp":"2026-06-25T06:04:20.919Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_vbzelk5s3hde_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Usage: opencli tiktok <command> [args] [options]\n\ncomment, creator-videos, explore, follow, following, friends, like, live, notifications, profile,\nsave, search, unfollow, unlike, unsave, user\n\nCommands:\n  comment <url> <text>       [write] Post a comment on a TikTok video\n  creator-videos [options]   [read] TikTok Studio creator content list (views/likes/comments/saves/shares)\n  explore [options]          [read] Get trending TikTok videos from the recommend feed via page-context APIs\n  follow <username>          [write] Follow a TikTok user by username\n  following [options]        [read] List accounts the logged-in user follows on TikTok via page-context APIs\n  friends [options]          [read] Get TikTok friend / who-to-follow suggestions via page-context APIs\n  like <url>                 [write] Like a TikTok video\n  live [options]             [read] Browse TikTok live streams via page-context APIs\n  notifications [options]    [read] Read TikTok inbox notifications (likes, comments, mentions, followers) via page-context APIs\n  profile <username>         [read] Get TikTok user profile info\n  save <url>                 [write] Add a TikTok video to Favorites\n  search <query> [options]   [read] Search TikTok videos\n  unfollow <username>        [write] Unfollow a TikTok user by username\n  unlike <url>               [write] Unlike a TikTok video\n  unsave <url>               [write] Remove a TikTok video from Favorites\n  user <username> [options]  [read] Get recent videos from a TikTok user via page-context APIs\n\nCommon options:\n  -f, --format <fmt>  Output format: table, plain, json, yaml, md, csv  default: table  choices: table, plain, json, yaml, md, csv\n  --trace <mode>      Trace capture: off, on, retain-on-failure  default: off  choices: off, on, retain-on-failure\n  -v, --verbose       Debug output  default: false\n  -h, --help          display help for command\n\nBrowser common options:\n  --window <mode>        Browser window mode: foreground or background  choices: foreground, background\n  --site-session <mode>  Adapter site session lifecycle: ephemeral or persistent  choices: ephemeral, persistent\n  --keep-tab <bool>      Keep the browser tab lease after the command finishes  choices: true, false\n\nAgent tip: use 'opencli tiktok --help -f yaml' to get all command args/options in one structured response.\n\n  Update available: v1.8.1 → v1.8.4\n  Run: npm install -g @jackwener/opencli\n\n===\n  amazon\n    bestsellers [cookie] — Amazon Best Sellers pages for category candidate discovery\n    discussion [cookie] — Amazon review summary and sample customer discussion from product review pages\n    movers-shakers [cookie] — Amazon Movers & Shakers pages for short-term growth signals\n    new-releases [cookie] — Amazon New Releases pages for early momentum discovery\n    offer [cookie] — Amazon seller, buy box, and fulfillment facts from the product page\n    product [cookie] — Amazon product page facts for candidate validation\n    search [cookie] — Amazon search results for product discovery and coarse filtering\n    product [cookie] — Read full product detail (price, rating, seller, delivery) for a Coupang product\n    marketplace-inbox [cookie] — List recent Facebook Marketplace buyer/seller conversations\n    marketplace-listings [cookie] — List your Facebook Marketplace seller listings\n    top-sellers [public] — Steam top selling games\n  tiktok\n    comment [cookie] — Post a comment on a TikTok video\n    creator-videos [cookie] — TikTok Studio creator content list (views/likes/comments/saves/shares)\n    explore [cookie] — Get trending TikTok videos from the recommend feed via page-context APIs\n    follow [cookie] — Follow a TikTok user by username\n    following [cookie] — List accounts the logged-in user follows on TikTok via page-context APIs\n    friends [cookie] — Get TikTok friend / who-to-follow suggestions via page-context APIs\n    like [cookie] — Like a TikTok video"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1163,"aggregated":"Usage: opencli tiktok <command> [args] [options]\n\ncomment, creator-videos, explore, follow, following, friends, like, live, notifications, profile,\nsave, search, unfollow, unlike, unsave, user\n\nCommands:\n  comment <url> <text>       [write] Post a comment on a TikTok video\n  creator-videos [options]   [read] TikTok Studio creator content list (views/likes/comments/saves/shares)\n  explore [options]          [read] Get trending TikTok videos from the recommend feed via page-context APIs\n  follow <username>          [write] Follow a TikTok user by username\n  following [options]        [read] List accounts the logged-in user follows on TikTok via page-context APIs\n  friends [options]          [read] Get TikTok friend / who-to-follow suggestions via page-context APIs\n  like <url>                 [write] Like a TikTok video\n  live [options]             [read] Browse TikTok live streams via page-context APIs\n  notifications [options]    [read] Read TikTok inbox notifications (likes, comments, mentions, followers) via page-context APIs\n  profile <username>         [read] Get TikTok user profile info\n  save <url>                 [write] Add a TikTok video to Favorites\n  search <query> [options]   [read] Search TikTok videos\n  unfollow <username>        [write] Unfollow a TikTok user by username\n  unlike <url>               [write] Unlike a TikTok video\n  unsave <url>               [write] Remove a TikTok video from Favorites\n  user <username> [options]  [read] Get recent videos from a TikTok user via page-context APIs\n\nCommon options:\n  -f, --format <fmt>  Output format: table, plain, json, yaml, md, csv  default: table  choices: table, plain, json, yaml, md, csv\n  --trace <mode>      Trace capture: off, on, retain-on-failure  default: off  choices: off, on, retain-on-failure\n  -v, --verbose       Debug output  default: false\n  -h, --help          display help for command\n\nBrowser common options:\n  --window <mode>        Browser window mode: foreground or background  choices: foreground, background\n  --site-session <mode>  Adapter site session lifecycle: ephemeral or persistent  choices: ephemeral, persistent\n  --keep-tab <bool>      Keep the browser tab lease after the command finishes  choices: true, false\n\nAgent tip: use 'opencli tiktok --help -f yaml' to get all command args/options in one structured response.\n\n  Update available: v1.8.1 → v1.8.4\n  Run: npm install -g @jackwener/opencli\n\n===\n  amazon\n    bestsellers [cookie] — Amazon Best Sellers pages for category candidate discovery\n    discussion [cookie] — Amazon review summary and sample customer discussion from product review pages\n    movers-shakers [cookie] — Amazon Movers & Shakers pages for short-term growth signals\n    new-releases [cookie] — Amazon New Releases pages for early momentum discovery\n    offer [cookie] — Amazon seller, buy box, and fulfillment facts from the product page\n    product [cookie] — Amazon product page facts for candidate validation\n    search [cookie] — Amazon search results for product discovery and coarse filtering\n    product [cookie] — Read full product detail (price, rating, seller, delivery) for a Coupang product\n    marketplace-inbox [cookie] — List recent Facebook Marketplace buyer/seller conversations\n    marketplace-listings [cookie] — List your Facebook Marketplace seller listings\n    top-sellers [public] — Steam top selling games\n  tiktok\n    comment [cookie] — Post a comment on a TikTok video\n    creator-videos [cookie] — TikTok Studio creator content list (views/likes/comments/saves/shares)\n    explore [cookie] — Get trending TikTok videos from the recommend feed via page-context APIs\n    follow [cookie] — Follow a TikTok user by username\n    following [cookie] — List accounts the logged-in user follows on TikTok via page-context APIs\n    friends [cookie] — Get TikTok friend / who-to-follow suggestions via page-context APIs\n    like [cookie] — Like a TikTok video","cwd":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1782367460909}}
{"type":"message","id":"676f0f00","parentId":"d7d35a21","timestamp":"2026-06-25T06:04:30.481Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\n\n## 🪶 答案：opencli 暂时帮不上 TK 后台\n\n**好消息：**\n- opencli 装好了（`/home/halei/.npm-global/bin/opencli`）\n- 它有 148 个网站适配器，覆盖了抖音、小红书、淘宝、京东、亚马逊等\n- 对**普通 TikTok**（视频/创作者/搜索）有现成命令\n\n**坏消息：**\n- **没有 `tiktok-shop` 适配器**——只有 `tiktok`（普通版）\n- 普通版只能：发评论、点赞、刷推荐流，**抓不到 seller center 数据**\n- 其他电商平台也缺：amazon 有、shopee 缺、tiktok-shop 缺\n\n---\n\n## 🔑 那我建议怎么走\n\n**主路径：OpenClaw 自带 `browser` 工具 + 自写 skill**\n- 通用、灵活、能跑所有未适配网站\n- 一个 `tk-shop` skill 搞定所有后台操作（登录、抓数据、导出、订单）\n\n**辅助路径：opencli 用作快速通道**\n- 后面如果 opencli 出了 tiktok-shop 适配器，**秒接入**\n- 在此之前，把它当**普通 TikTok 数据源**（达人视频、竞品视频），给选品大师/content 用\n\n---\n\n**我用 opencli doctor 测一下连通性，看它的浏览器桥能不能跟我们后面要建的 tk-shop profile 共用。** 给你完整方案："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ceepd5i0i8hy_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"opencli doctor 2>&1 | head -30\necho \"===\"\nopencli profile list 2>&1 | head -20"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":973,"output":359,"cacheRead":80849,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":82181,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782367460939,"responseId":"068bf7e59b745ce9f93fc6e94787c9ab","responseModel":"MiniMax-M3"}}
{"type":"message","id":"cefd1034","parentId":"676f0f00","timestamp":"2026-06-25T06:04:40.012Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_ceepd5i0i8hy_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"opencli v1.8.1 doctor (node v22.22.2)\n\n[OK] Daemon: running on port 19825 (v1.8.1)\n[MISSING] Extension: not connected\n[FAIL] Connectivity: failed (Browser Bridge extension not connected)\n\nIssues:\n  • Daemon is running but the Chrome/Chromium extension is not connected.\nIf the extension is already installed, try: opencli daemon restart\nIf the extension is not installed:\n  1. Download from https://github.com/jackwener/opencli/releases\n  2. Open chrome://extensions/ → Enable Developer Mode\n  3. Click \"Load unpacked\" → select the extension folder\n  • Browser connectivity test failed: Browser Bridge extension not connected\n\n  Update available: v1.8.1 → v1.8.4\n  Run: npm install -g @jackwener/opencli\n\n===\nNo Browser Bridge profiles connected.\nOpen a Chrome profile with the OpenCLI extension installed, then run opencli profile list again.\n\n  Update available: v1.8.1 → v1.8.4\n  Run: npm install -g @jackwener/opencli"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":9242,"aggregated":"opencli v1.8.1 doctor (node v22.22.2)\n\n[OK] Daemon: running on port 19825 (v1.8.1)\n[MISSING] Extension: not connected\n[FAIL] Connectivity: failed (Browser Bridge extension not connected)\n\nIssues:\n  • Daemon is running but the Chrome/Chromium extension is not connected.\nIf the extension is already installed, try: opencli daemon restart\nIf the extension is not installed:\n  1. Download from https://github.com/jackwener/opencli/releases\n  2. Open chrome://extensions/ → Enable Developer Mode\n  3. Click \"Load unpacked\" → select the extension folder\n  • Browser connectivity test failed: Browser Bridge extension not connected\n\n  Update available: v1.8.1 → v1.8.4\n  Run: npm install -g @jackwener/opencli\n\n===\nNo Browser Bridge profiles connected.\nOpen a Chrome profile with the OpenCLI extension installed, then run opencli profile list again.\n\n  Update available: v1.8.1 → v1.8.4\n  Run: npm install -g @jackwener/opencli","cwd":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1782367480009}}
{"type":"message","id":"248cd021","parentId":"cefd1034","timestamp":"2026-06-25T06:04:45.405Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\n\n## 🪶 完整结论\n\n**opencli 现状：**\n- ✅ 装了，daemon 在跑（端口 19825）\n- ❌ **Chrome 扩展没装、没连接**——需要手动装个 Chrome 扩展才能用\n- ❌ 没有 tiktok-shop 适配器\n\n**所以最终方案不变：**\n\n**主路径**：OpenClaw `browser` 工具（自带的，可视化） + 我写的 `tk-shop` skill\n- 不用装扩展\n- 直接驱动我们刚建的 `tk-shop-main` profile\n- 所有 agent 都能用\n\n**opencli 留作辅助**（不耽误事）：\n- 等 tiktok-shop 适配器出了，无缝接入\n- 普通 TikTok 数据可以给选品大师用（看竞品视频）\n\n---\n\n**你回我\"开干\"，我就启动独立 Chrome 让你登一次 TK。** opencli 这事我先放着，不影响主计划。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":286,"output":202,"cacheRead":82162,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":82650,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782367480025,"responseId":"068bf7f8d8b2036f948c4a9e62a5143c","responseModel":"MiniMax-M3"}}
