{"type":"message","id":"bba6fe65","parentId":"a737df96","timestamp":"2026-06-25T06:18:08.081Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**有大问题——gateway 实际是 hermes 容器（pid 517708），而我以为是 18789 的 openclaw gateway。** 这是两个独立的东西：\n\n- **port 18789** = OpenClaw 自己的 gateway（systemd 管理，pid 不知道）\n- **pid 517708** = hermes agent gateway\n\n**我刚才用 `gateway` 工具重启的是 OpenClaw 自己的 gateway（port 18789），跟 hermes 无关。** 但是我修改的 openclaw.json 是 OpenClaw 的——所以理论上 OpenClaw gateway 应该读到了。\n\n让我直接 verify 一下 OpenClaw 自己的 gateway 是否还在跑。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_34o06h2je3g2_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ps aux | grep \"openclaw\" | grep -v grep | head -10\necho \"===\"\n# 看 18789 端口\nss -tlnp 2>/dev/null | grep -E \"18789|18901\"\necho \"===\"\n# OpenClaw gateway 进程\nps aux | grep -E \"18789|gateway --port\" | grep -v grep | head -5"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":371,"output":249,"cacheRead":95958,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":96578,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782368282652,"responseId":"068bfb1b172c5656b53aec473f789f06","responseModel":"MiniMax-M3"}}
