{"type":"message","id":"a361e6f3","parentId":"2acd9509","timestamp":"2026-06-25T06:20:53.894Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**回到原点。** 现在用务实方案：\n\n**直接用 exec 启动一个独立 Chrome（CDP 端口 18901）→ browser 工具 attach 上。** 不用改 openclaw.json。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_02ttryndztq2_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 1. 确认 profile 目录\nls -la /home/halei/.openclaw/browser/tk-HUG-VN/\necho \"---\"\n# 2. 启动独立 Chrome，CDP 端口 18901，color 紫色（用 --window-name 实现标识）\nnohup google-chrome \\\n  --user-data-dir=/home/halei/.openclaw/browser/tk-HUG-VN \\\n  --profile-directory=\"Default\" \\\n  --no-first-run \\\n  --no-default-browser-check \\\n  --disable-background-timer-throttling \\\n  --disable-backgrounding-occluded-windows \\\n  --disable-renderer-backgrounding \\\n  --window-size=1440,900 \\\n  --window-position=100,80 \\\n  --remote-debugging-port=18901 \\\n  --remote-debugging-address=127.0.0.1 \\\n  --window-name=\"tk-HUG-VN 💜 Heat Up Glow\" \\\n  \"https://seller.tiktok.com/portal\" \\\n  > /home/halei/.openclaw/browser/tk-HUG-VN/chrome.log 2>&1 &\n\nCHROME_PID=$!\necho \"Chrome PID: $CHROME_PID\"\nsleep 4\n# 验证 CDP 端口\nss -tlnp 2>/dev/null | grep 18901 | head -3\necho \"---\"\n# 验证 CDP 端点\ncurl -s --max-time 3 http://127.0.0.1:18901/json/version 2>&1 | head -10"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":51,"output":394,"cacheRead":103282,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":103727,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782368447574,"responseId":"068bfbc081f1720f732973dedd445908","responseModel":"MiniMax-M3"}}
