{"type":"message","id":"ca90bf15","parentId":"94360017","timestamp":"2026-06-25T06:21:16.555Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_dp7m8yn497ql_1","toolName":"browser","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"enabled\": true,\n  \"profile\": \"openclaw\",\n  \"driver\": \"openclaw\",\n  \"transport\": \"cdp\",\n  \"running\": true,\n  \"cdpReady\": true,\n  \"cdpHttp\": true,\n  \"pageReady\": true,\n  \"pid\": 1728052,\n  \"cdpPort\": 18800,\n  \"cdpUrl\": \"http://127.0.0.1:18800\",\n  \"chosenBrowser\": \"chrome\",\n  \"detectedBrowser\": \"chrome\",\n  \"detectedExecutablePath\": \"/usr/bin/google-chrome-stable\",\n  \"detectError\": null,\n  \"userDataDir\": \"/home/halei/.openclaw/browser/openclaw/user-data\",\n  \"color\": \"#FF4500\",\n  \"headless\": false,\n  \"headlessSource\": \"config\",\n  \"noSandbox\": false,\n  \"executablePath\": null,\n  \"attachOnly\": false\n}"}],"details":{"enabled":true,"profile":"openclaw","driver":"openclaw","transport":"cdp","running":true,"cdpReady":true,"cdpHttp":true,"pageReady":true,"pid":1728052,"cdpPort":18800,"cdpUrl":"http://127.0.0.1:18800","chosenBrowser":"chrome","detectedBrowser":"chrome","detectedExecutablePath":"/usr/bin/google-chrome-stable","detectError":null,"userDataDir":"/home/halei/.openclaw/browser/openclaw/user-data","color":"#FF4500","headless":false,"headlessSource":"config","noSandbox":false,"executablePath":null,"attachOnly":false},"isError":false,"timestamp":1782368476552}}
{"type":"message","id":"03033595","parentId":"ca90bf15","timestamp":"2026-06-25T06:21:27.149Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**OpenClaw 启动了一个新的 Chrome（pid 1728052, port 18800）——但不是我们那个 tk-HUG-VN。** 它用自己的 userDataDir（`/home/halei/.openclaw/browser/openclaw/user-data`）。\n\n**这是 OpenClaw 的\"managed browser\"模式**：自己起一个 Chrome，我们得让它接 18901 这个已经开好的——但它不支持 cdpUrl 注入。\n\n---\n\n## 🪶 现实方案\n\nOpenClaw 的 `browser` 工具**只能管自己启动的 Chrome**。它不让我\"attach 到外部 18901 Chrome\"。\n\n**两条路：**\n\n**A. 让 OpenClaw 自己管理 tk-HUG-VN Chrome**\n- 用它默认的 `openclaw` profile（已有 userDataDir）\n- 你登一次 TK，cookie 存在 `/home/halei/.openclaw/browser/openclaw/user-data`\n- **缺点**：跟其他 OpenClaw 自动化操作混用\n\n**B. 我自己用脚本驱动 18901 Chrome（绕过 OpenClaw browser 工具）**\n- 写 Python 脚本用 CDP 协议直接调 18901\n- agent 通过 `exec` 调脚本\n- **优点**：完全独立隔离\n- **缺点**：自己写 CDP 客户端，工作量大\n\n**我建议 A**：先让 OpenClaw 的 openclaw profile 进 TK，然后 cron 后台跑我们的 `tk-shop` 脚本，**OpenClaw 的 openclaw profile 就作为\"驱动浏览器\"，而数据/操作走我们写的脚本**。\n\n**先验证 HALEI 能不能看到那个 18901 浏览器窗口登录 TK。** 你现在屏幕上看得到新开的 Chrome 吗？"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_31pkr7mj8oc2_1","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"screenshot","profile":"openclaw"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":236,"output":394,"cacheRead":105117,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":105747,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782368477068,"responseId":"068bfbddd898e403d0446ab2068a4e1c","responseModel":"MiniMax-M3"}}
