{"type":"message","id":"ed7ccf95","parentId":"97ed7d30","timestamp":"2026-06-25T06:29:58.993Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**你是对的，我刚才判断错了。** 重新看那张截图——**我用的是 OpenClaw 自己 default chrome 的视觉模式**（顶部图标、profile 切换菜单都是 OpenClaw 的样式），不是真独立的。\n\n**实际情况是这样：**\n\n```\nOpenClaw 自己的 Chrome (18800) → 它自带的 user-data-dir → 不是我们 heat-up-glow\n我 exec 启的 Chrome (18901)    → heat-up-glow profile → 才是我们想要的\n```\n\n但**你看到那个菜单/图标的那个窗口是 OpenClaw 的 18800，不是我们的 18901**。我之前没意识到这点——`browser start` 调的是 OpenClaw 自己的 Chrome，**跟我们 18901 是两回事**。\n\n让我立刻纠正——把 OpenClaw 那套关掉，只留 18901："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_019efd78956a7b409e999a37","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 看现在有几个 Chrome 在跑\nps -ef | grep \"google-chrome\" | grep -v grep | grep -v crashpad | head -10\necho \"===\"\necho \"18901 (我们 heat-up-glow):\"\nss -tlnp 2>/dev/null | grep 18901\necho \"===\"\necho \"18800 (OpenClaw 自带):\"\nss -tlnp 2>/dev/null | grep 18800\necho \"===\"\necho \"9222 (系统 chrome):\"\nss -tlnp 2>/dev/null | grep 9222"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":2158,"output":325,"cacheRead":110336,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":112819,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782368971806,"responseId":"068bfdcc82ae72489062476c32ffa548","responseModel":"MiniMax-M3"}}
