{"type":"message","id":"42edc33f","parentId":"aae7380e","timestamp":"2026-06-25T06:30:26.363Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**18901 Chrome 现在有两个标签页：**\n1. `chrome://settings/help`（设置页）\n2. `https://seller.tiktokshopglobalselling.com/account/login`（**TK 登录页，已经加载！**）\n\n所以 18901 Chrome **是好的**，那个 TK 登录页就在那。**但你截图里看到的那个\"OpenClaw 风格\"的窗口，是之前 OpenClaw 自己 18800 启的 Chrome——已经关掉了。**\n\n---\n\n## 🪶 现在情况\n\n**18901 Chrome 是我们独立的 profile（heat-up-glow）**——它已经在加载 TK 登录页了。\n\n你截图里的那个\"OpenClaw 头像/菜单\"的窗口是 **OpenClaw 自己 18800 Chrome 跑的时候的样子**——现在已经停了。\n\n---\n\n## 现在请你做\n\n**1. 看 Ubuntu 桌面现在还有什么 Chrome 窗口**\n- 如果**只有 1 个** `heat-up-glow` 标题的窗口 → 就是 18901，TK 登录页应该在\n- 如果**还有别的** → 截图给我看\n\n**2. 切到 TK 登录页那个标签**（`https://seller.tiktokshopglobalselling.com/account/login`）\n\n**3. 点 \"邮箱登录\"**\n\n**4. 输账号密码**（`59330857cc@gmail.com` / `Lc@295467`）\n\n**5. 首次邮箱验证码 → 你查邮箱告诉我**\n\n---\n\n**确认：现在只剩 18901 那一个 Chrome 了吧？** 你看下桌面跟我说。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":204,"output":323,"cacheRead":113024,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":113551,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782369015648,"responseId":"068bfdf89aa758a5d22812a51ccf6595","responseModel":"MiniMax-M3"}}
