{"type":"message","id":"760a38a9","parentId":"84974ed3","timestamp":"2026-06-25T06:43:46.248Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**一个 profile 一个站点。** 你几个站点就几个 profile。\n\n```\n~/.openclaw/browser/\n├── tk-sg/      ← 新加坡\n├── tk-my/      ← 马来\n├── tk-th/      ← 泰国\n├── tk-vn/      ← 越南\n├── tk-ph/      ← 菲律宾\n└── ...\n```\n\n命名规则：`tk-{站点代码}`，独立 cookie、独立登录态。**不混用。**\n\nAgent 调度时按站点取对应 profile，互不串。\n\n---\n\n**现在告诉我：你的 5 个站点是哪几个？**\n\n我按这个命名建文件夹。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":1050,"output":127,"cacheRead":72832,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":74009,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782367129581,"responseId":"068bf69a829d63b0fc031a29c57cea5c","responseModel":"MiniMax-M3"}}
