{"type":"message","id":"641a37e6","parentId":"fa6cfe04","timestamp":"2026-06-25T06:43:46.249Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**理解了。** 站点不是问题，右上角一键切。**真正要分的是\"账号\"**——一个店铺一个登录态。\n\n**逻辑：**\n\n```\n一个 agent 服务一个类目/店铺账号\n```\n\n不是按站点分，是按**登录账号**分。因为同一个 seller center 右上角切站点，是同一个 cookie 域、不同 store_id。\n\n---\n\n**所以 profile 命名改一下：**\n\n```\n~/.openclaw/browser/\n├── tk-shop-A/    ← 类目A 店铺账号\n├── tk-shop-B/    ← 类目B 店铺账号\n└── ...\n```\n\nAgent 接任务时，**绑定一个固定的 profile**，自动登录自己的店。\n\n---\n\n**你直接告诉我：你现在有 1 个还是多个店铺账号？**\n\n- **1 个账号管所有类目** → 1 个 profile，9 个 agent 共享\n- **多个账号**（不同公司/不同主账号）→ 几个账号几个 profile\n\n定了就开干。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":73565,"output":203,"cacheRead":498,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":74266,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782367175823,"responseId":"068bf6c8ed98b378521c401659a179d7","responseModel":"MiniMax-M3"}}
