{"type":"message","id":"48695688","parentId":"18ee7e5b","timestamp":"2026-06-25T06:43:46.250Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**等等——实际 openclaw.json 里根本没有 profiles 那段。** 截图里看到的应该是某个别的配置文件（可能是 clawpanel.json 或者 agent-orchestrator 的某个配置）。我先核对。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_019efd6b576a723188af0269","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"===== search where browser.profiles exists =====\"\ngrep -rl \"browser\" /home/halei/.openclaw/openclaw.json /home/halei/.openclaw/clawpanel.json /home/halei/.openclaw/openclaw.json.bak 2>/dev/null | head -5\necho \"---\"\necho \"===== look at clawpanel.json =====\"\ncat /home/halei/.openclaw/clawpanel.json 2>/dev/null | python3 -c \"\nimport json, sys\ntry:\n    d = json.load(sys.stdin)\n    print('keys:', list(d.keys())[:20])\n    if 'browser' in d:\n        print('browser:', json.dumps(d['browser'], indent=2))\nexcept: pass\n\"\necho \"---\"\necho \"===== search all configs for browser profiles =====\"\ngrep -l \"18801\\|18802\\|cdpPort\" /home/halei/.openclaw/*.json 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":42,"output":266,"cacheRead":85888,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":86196,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782368119397,"responseId":"068bfa77f86325efce97ba341e6155ca","responseModel":"MiniMax-M3"}}
