{"type":"message","id":"a9309aff","parentId":"27934d27","timestamp":"2026-06-25T06:43:46.251Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**完美。** `browser.profiles` 是 OpenClaw 6.9 的官方配置项。**截图里那个格式基本是对的**——我按官方 schema 来写就行。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_d3fq6e7kwiqn_1","name":"gateway","arguments":{"action":"config.schema.lookup","path":"browser.profiles"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":2753,"output":77,"cacheRead":87339,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":90169,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782368190538,"responseId":"068bfabf431689255d88d1a0131a1794","responseModel":"MiniMax-M3"}}
{"type":"message","id":"84f0c981","parentId":"a9309aff","timestamp":"2026-06-25T06:43:46.251Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_d3fq6e7kwiqn_1","toolName":"gateway","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[... 4974 more characters truncated; rerun with narrower args if need"}],"details":{"ok":true,"result":{"path":"browser.profiles","schema":{"type":"object","title":"Browser Profiles","description":"Named browser profile connection map used for explicit routing to CDP ports or URLs with optional metadata. Keep profile names consistent and avoid overlapping endpoint definitions.","additionalProperties":{"type":"object","additionalProperties":false,"properties":{"cdpPort":{"type":"integer","minimum":1,"maximum":65535,"title":"Browser Profile CDP Port","description":"Per-profile local CDP port used when connecting to browser instances by port instead of URL. Use unique ports per profile to avoid connection collisions."},"cdpUrl":{"type":"string","title":"Browser Profile CDP URL","description":"Per-profile CDP/DevTools endpoint URL used for explicit browser routing by profile name. Use this for remote CDP hosts, tunnels, or existing-session profiles that should attach through a running Chrome DevTools endpoint."},"userDataDir":{"type":"string","title":"Browser Profile User Data Dir","description":"Per-profile Chromium user data directory for existing-session attachment through Chrome DevTools MCP. Use this for Brave, Edge, Chromium, or non-default Chrome profiles when the built-in auto-connect path would pick the wrong browser data directory on the selected host or browser node. Paths starting with ~ expand to the OS home directory."},"mcpCommand":{"type":"string","title":"Browser Profile Chrome MCP Command","description":"Per-profile Chrome DevTools MCP command for existing-session attachment. Defaults to npx."},"mcpArgs":{"type":"array","title":"Browser Profile Chrome MCP Args","description":"Extra per-profile Chrome DevTools MCP arguments for existing-session attachment, such as --no-usage-statistics. Endpoint arguments here override the built-in auto-connect or browser URL selection.","items":{"type":"string"}},"driver":{"title":"Browser Profile Driver","description":"Per-profile browser driver mode. Use \"openclaw\" (or legacy \"clawd\") for CDP-based profiles, or use \"existing-session\" for Chrome DevTools MCP attachment on the selected host or browser node.","anyOf":[{"type":"string","const":"openclaw"},{"type":"string","const":"clawd"},{"type":"string","const":"existing-session"}]},"headless":{"type":"boolean","title":"Browser Profile Headless Mode","description":"Per-profile headless override for locally launched browser instances. Use this when one profile should stay headless without forcing browser.headless for every other profile."},"executablePath":{"type":"string","title":"Browser Profile Executable Path","description":"Per-profile browser executable path for locally launched managed browser profiles. Overrides browser.executablePath and accepts paths starting with ~ for the OS home directory."},"attachOnly":{"type":"boolean","title":"Browser Profile Attach-only Mode","description":"Per-profile attach-only override that skips local browser launch and only attaches to an existing CDP endpoint. Useful when one profile is externally managed but others are locally launched."},"color":{"type":"string","pattern":"^#?[0-9a-fA-F]{6}$","title":"Browser Profile Accent Color","description":"Per-profile accent color for visual differentiation in dashboards and browser-related UI hints. Use distinct colors for high-signal operator recognition of active profiles."}}}},"reloadKind":"restart","hint":{"label":"Browser Profiles","help":"Named browser profile connection map used for explicit routing to CDP ports or URLs with optional metadata. Keep profile names consistent and avoid overlapping endpoint definitions.","tags":["storage"]},"hintPath":"browser.profiles","children":[{"key":"*","path":"browser.profiles.*","type":"object","required":false,"hasChildren":true,"reloadKind":"restart"}]}},"isError":false,"timestamp":1782368195589}}
{"type":"message","id":"2a9690ad","parentId":"84f0c981","timestamp":"2026-06-25T06:43:46.251Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**字段确认完毕。** OpenClaw 6.9 的 `browser.profiles.*` 支持：\n- `cdpPort`、`cdpUrl`、`userDataDir`、`color`（你截图里那些都对）\n- 还多了 `headless`、`executablePath`、`attachOnly`、`driver`、`mcpCommand`、`mcpArgs`\n\n**注意：profile 对象里没有 `label` 字段**——截图里那个 `\"label\"` 是别人 schema 加的扩展，我们**不能用**。我去掉。\n\n---\n\n## 🪶 开工：HUG-VN profile 写入 openclaw.json\n\n**配置：**\n- profile name: `tk-HUG-VN`\n- cdpPort: **18901**（截图里 18801/18802 已被占）\n- color: **#A155F0**（紫色 = Heat Up Glow 时尚感）\n- userDataDir: `/home/halei/.openclaw/browser/tk-HUG-VN`\n- headless: **false**（你 14:02 选的可视化）\n\n先建 profile 目录，然后改 openclaw.json。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_hteey1d3bn1v_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mkdir -p /home/halei/.openclaw/browser/tk-HUG-VN\nls -la /home/halei/.openclaw/browser/tk-HUG-VN/"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_hteey1d3bn1v_2","name":"gateway","arguments":{"action":"config.patch","raw":"{\n  \"browser\": {\n    \"headless\": false,\n    \"defaultProfile\": \"tk-HUG-VN\",\n    \"profiles\": {\n      \"tk-HUG-VN\": {\n        \"userDataDir\": \"/home/halei/.openclaw/browser/tk-HUG-VN\",\n        \"cdpPort\": 18901,\n        \"color\": \"#A155F0\",\n        \"headless\": false\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}","reason":"添加 TK HUG-VN 浏览器 profile（Heat Up Glow - VN 发饰店铺）","note":"已添加 tk-HUG-VN 浏览器 profile，重启后生效"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":1032,"output":464,"cacheRead":90155,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":91651,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782368195610,"responseId":"068bfac45a5e374c1979cc819ea72b76","responseModel":"MiniMax-M3"}}
