{"type":"message","id":"4900b6a0","parentId":"ba8f6bdd","timestamp":"2026-06-25T06:43:46.252Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**找到根因！** Doctor 报告：\n```\nbrowser.profiles.tk-HUG-VN: Invalid key in record\n```\n\n我配置的 profile 字段被 schema 拒绝了。**`userDataDir`、`cdpPort`、`color`、`headless` 都没错，但 OpenClaw 的 internal 校验说\"Invalid key in record\"——可能是 `additionalProperties: false` 跟某个字段冲突。**\n\n让我重新检查 schema 看哪个字段不被允许："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ayb0ekng720n_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 << 'EOF'\n# 逐个试，看哪个字段不让\nimport subprocess, json\n\nbase = {\"userDataDir\": \"/home/halei/.openclaw/browser/tk-HUG-VN\"}\nfor field in [\"cdpPort\", \"color\", \"headless\", \"executablePath\", \"attachOnly\", \"driver\", \"mcpCommand\", \"mcpArgs\", \"cdpUrl\"]:\n    test = {**base, field: 18901 if field==\"cdpPort\" else \"#A155F0\" if field==\"color\" else False if field==\"headless\" else \"test\"}\n    cfg = {\n        \"browser\": {\n            \"headless\": False,\n            \"defaultProfile\": \"tk-HUG-VN\",\n            \"profiles\": {\n                \"tk-HUG-VN\": test\n            }\n        }\n    }\n    # 写文件\n    with open(\"/home/halei/.openclaw/openclaw.json\") as f:\n        d = json.load(f)\n    d[\"browser\"] = cfg[\"browser\"]\n    with open(\"/home/halei/.openclaw/openclaw.json\", \"w\") as f:\n        json.dump(d, f, indent=2, ensure_ascii=False)\n    \n    # 触发校验\n    r = subprocess.run([\"openclaw\", \"config\", \"validate\"], capture_output=True, text=True, timeout=8)\n    err = r.stderr + r.stdout\n    if \"Invalid\" in err and field in err:\n        print(f\"❌ {field}: rejected\")\n    elif \"Invalid\" in err and \"browser.profiles\" in err:\n        print(f\"⚠️  {field}: 可能 OK，但其他字段问题\")\n    else:\n        print(f\"✅ {field}: OK\")\nEOF"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":352,"output":488,"cacheRead":97286,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":98126,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782368330254,"responseId":"068bfb4b53c6c90416b61a367356aea2","responseModel":"MiniMax-M3"}}
