    Webhook helpers and integrations\n\nExamples:\n  openclaw onboard\n    Run guided setup for a local Gateway, workspace, auth, and channels.\n  openclaw setup\n    Create the baseline config, workspace, and session folders.\n  openclaw configure\n    Change models, Gateway, channels, plugins, skills, and health checks.\n  openclaw status\n    Check Gateway, channel, model, and recent-session status.\n  openclaw doctor --fix\n    Repair common config, service, plugin, and channel problems.\n  openclaw channels add\n    Add or update a chat channel account with guided prompts.\n  openclaw channels status\n    See connected messaging accounts and login state.\n  openclaw --dev gateway\n    Run a dev Gateway (isolated state/config) on ws://127.0.0.1:19001.\n  openclaw gateway run --force\n    Start the Gateway and replace anything bound to its port.\n  openclaw models status\n    Show model/provider auth health before running agents.\n  openclaw plugins list\n    Inspect enabled, disabled, and installed plugins.\n  openclaw agent --to +15555550123 --message \"Run summary\" --deliver\n    Run one agent turn through the Gateway and optionally deliver the reply.\n  openclaw message send --channel telegram --target @mychat --message \"Hi\"\n    Send via your Telegram bot.\n\nDocs: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli\n\n","name":"openclaw create-profile"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1782368437605}}
{"type":"message","id":"4cd4934c","parentId":"d5cec2a0","timestamp":"2026-06-25T06:43:46.252Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**关键错误：**\n\n```\n[plugins] openclaw-dist failed to load from /home/halei/.openclaw/extensions/openclaw_dist/index.js: SyntaxError: Unexpected identifier 'Promise'\n```\n\n**OpenClaw 自己的扩展（openclaw_dist）加载失败**——这是 `browser` 子命令的来源。所以 `openclaw browser`/`create-profile` 都不可用。\n\n---\n\n## 重新评估方向\n\n我刚才查到的 schema 和 CLI 都是 OpenClaw 文档里的，**但**实际装的 6.8 版本 + 当前扩展损坏，**这条路暂时不通。**\n\n**回到务实方案：**\n\n**走 OpenClaw 的 `browser` 工具**（model 层），不靠 openclaw.json profiles 段。\n\n- 之前用 `browser` 工具 + `profile=\"tk-HUG-VN\"` 报错说\"Profile not found\"——但报错信息里说\"Available profiles: openclaw, user\"\n- 也就是说 OpenClaw 6.8 自带 2 个默认 profile：**openclaw** 和 **user**\n- 我们的目标：让 `tk-HUG-VN` 也成为可识别的 profile\n\n**最简单的路：用现成的 `user` profile，但指定我们的 userDataDir。** Browser 工具支持 `profile=\"user\"` 默认走用户主目录的 Chrome。\n\n但我想要的是**干净隔离**——不污染你日常 Chrome。\n\n**让我用另一种方式启动：** 直接用 exec 启动一个独立 Chrome（port 18901），然后用 `browser` 工具的 `profile=\"openclaw\"` 模式 attach 上去。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_lvdt7nv5bi55_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 先把 openclaw.json 恢复成原始状态，避免污染\ncp /home/halei/.openclaw/openclaw.json.bak-tk-browser-20260625 /home/halei/.openclaw/openclaw.json\necho \"openclaw.json restored\"\npython3 -c \"\nimport json\nwith open('/home/halei/.openclaw/openclaw.json') as f:\n    d = json.load(f)\nprint('browser section:', json.dumps(d.get('browser', {}), indent=2, ensure_ascii=False))\n\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":782,"output":464,"cacheRead":102054,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":103300,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782368437634,"responseId":"068bfbb676c7d2e2ef3e585707332e23","responseModel":"MiniMax-M3"}}
