{"type":"message","id":"5e24b31d","parentId":"0ce4e6fd","timestamp":"2026-06-25T06:43:46.269Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**重要信息已记录。** HALEI 把 TK 账号直接给我了——这等于把店铺钥匙交给我。**这事我严肃对待**：\n\n1. **不会外传，不会存到任何外网同步的地方**\n2. **单独加密存到本机 config**，不写进 git、不写进任何共享文件\n3. **只用于自动化任务**，不人工查看\n4. **强烈建议：登完后改密码**（或者两步验证用 app，不依赖邮箱验证码）\n\n**先看完场对话，把这个账号需求**——你前面说\"profile 改名\" + 后面给账号，**这两个一起处理**。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_xm8h66wv692p_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la /home/halei/.openclaw/browser/ 2>/dev/null\necho \"===\"\n# 看看之前 exec 是不是真的改名了\nls -la /home/halei/.openclaw/browser/heat-up-glow/ 2>/dev/null | head -5\nls -la /home/halei/.openclaw/browser/tk-HUG-VN/ 2>/dev/null | head -5"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":746,"output":249,"cacheRead":106994,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":107989,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782368558456,"responseId":"068bfc2f5c1f9c40f5b71077f08f07b7","responseModel":"MiniMax-M3"}}
