{"type":"message","id":"7bb0c029","parentId":"953290a1","timestamp":"2026-06-25T06:43:46.270Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**`heat-up-glow` profile 已就位**，里面的数据保留（之前那几次 Chrome 跑过加载了一些必要文件）。**用你给的账号启动新 Chrome：**\n\n**1. 改写启动脚本，加入账号登录**\n\n`https://seller.tiktokshopglobalselling.com/` 是 TK 跨全球卖家中心，比 `seller.tiktok.com/portal` 对。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_jvj0uai184bn_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/home/halei/.openclaw/browser/heat-up-glow/launch.sh","content":"#!/bin/bash\n# Heat Up Glow 店铺专用 Chrome profile\n# - 独立 user-data-dir，cookie 隔离\n# - 1 个 profile 服务多站点（TK 后台右上角切换）\n# - 18901 端口固定给这个 profile\n\nset -e\n\nPROFILE_DIR=\"/home/halei/.openclaw/browser/heat-up-glow\"\nLAUNCH_URL=\"${1:-https://seller.tiktokshopglobalselling.com/}\"\nCDP_PORT=\"${CDP_PORT:-18901}\"\nLOG_FILE=\"$PROFILE_DIR/chrome.log\"\n\nmkdir -p \"$PROFILE_DIR\"\n\n# 杀掉旧实例（避免锁文件冲突）\npkill -9 -f \"user-data-dir=$PROFILE_DIR\" 2>/dev/null || true\nsleep 1\n\n# 启动 Chrome，远程调试端口\nnohup google-chrome \\\n  --user-data-dir=\"$PROFILE_DIR\" \\\n  --profile-directory=\"Default\" \\\n  --no-first-run \\\n  --no-default-browser-check \\\n  --disable-background-timer-throttling \\\n  --disable-backgrounding-occluded-windows \\\n  --disable-renderer-backgrounding \\\n  --window-size=1440,900 \\\n  --window-position=100,80 \\\n  --remote-debugging-port=\"$CDP_PORT\" \\\n  --remote-debugging-address=127.0.0.1 \\\n  --window-name=\"heat-up-glow 💜 Heat Up Glow (TK)\" \\\n  \"$LAUNCH_URL\" \\\n  > \"$LOG_FILE\" 2>&1 &\n\nCHROME_PID=$!\necho \"Chrome PID: $CHROME_PID\"\necho \"Profile:    $PROFILE_DIR\"\necho \"URL:        $LAUNCH_URL\"\necho \"CDP Port:   $CDP_PORT\"\necho \"CDP URL:    http://127.0.0.1:$CDP_PORT\"\necho \"\"\n\nsleep 3\nif kill -0 $CHROME_PID 2>/dev/null; then\n  echo \"✅ Chrome 已启动\"\n  echo \"\"\n  echo \"下一步：\"\n  echo \"  1. 浏览器自动打开 $LAUNCH_URL\"\n  echo \"  2. 看到登录页后，手动操作：\"\n  echo \"     a) 选择「邮箱登录」\"\n  echo \"     b) 账号：59330857cc@gmail.com\"\n  echo \"     c) 密码：Lc@295467\"\n  echo \"     d) 首次登录需要邮箱验证码（HALEI 提供）\"\n  echo \"     e) 登录后保持窗口打开，cookie 自动持久化\"\n  echo \"\"\n  echo \"  3. 后面所有 agent 都用端口 $CDP_PORT 复用此 session\"\nelse\n  echo \"❌ Chrome 启动失败，查看日志：\"\n  cat \"$LOG_FILE\"\n  exit 1\nfi\n"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_jvj0uai184bn_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"chmod +x /home/halei/.openclaw/browser/heat-up-glow/launch.sh\n# 删除 .log 旧文件，免得新进程写入失败\nrm -f /home/halei/.openclaw/browser/heat-up-glow/chrome.log\necho \"ready\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":287,"output":804,"cacheRead":109347,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":110438,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782368601415,"responseId":"068bfc5abf8aa7c7ecc40b28595f35f9","responseModel":"MiniMax-M3"}}
