{"type":"message","id":"189144a3","parentId":"de3d134c","timestamp":"2026-06-25T06:43:46.270Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**18901 Chrome 跑起来了，TK 登录页已经加载。** 窗口标题是 `heat-up-glow 💜 Heat Up Glow (TK)`。\n\n---\n\n## 🪶 HALEI 现在请你做\n\n**1. 看你的 Ubuntu 桌面**\n- 应该弹出**新 Chrome 窗口**（紫色标识 `heat-up-glow 💜 Heat Up Glow (TK)`）\n- 里面是 `https://seller.tiktokshopglobalselling.com/` 的登录页\n\n**2. 手动登录**\n- 点 **「邮箱登录」**\n- 账号：`59330857cc@gmail.com`\n- 密码：`Lc@295467`\n- 首次需要邮箱验证码 → 你去邮箱查一下，把验证码输进去\n\n**3. 登完之后**\n- 保持 Chrome 窗口**开着我**（不要关）——后续 agent 立刻复用这个 session\n- 或者你关掉也行，cookie 会持久化，下次启动自动恢复\n\n**我这边会一直等。** 你登上了就说一声\"ok\"，我去验证 9 个 agent 都能 attach 上这个 18901。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":136,"output":229,"cacheRead":111779,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":112144,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782368648000,"responseId":"068bfc88a34c0a2b302ceea312388e27","responseModel":"MiniMax-M3"}}
