{"type":"message","id":"8a03b038","parentId":"c1d6d180","timestamp":"2026-06-25T07:20:06.457Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**重启后没图形界面了。** 这是 headless 限制——你 Ubuntu 桌面可能没起来。**问题不在浏览器**——是 DISPLAY 环境变量没设。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_vqv7qih5nonj_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"DISPLAY=$DISPLAY\"\necho \"WAYLAND_DISPLAY=$WAYLAND_DISPLAY\"\necho \"---\"\nls /tmp/.X11-unix/ 2>/dev/null\necho \"---\"\n# 看 Xvfb / 桌面环境\nps aux | grep -iE \"Xorg|Xvfb|gdm|lightdm|wayland\" | grep -v grep | head -5\necho \"---\"\n# 看 X 端口\nss -tlnp 2>/dev/null | grep -E \":60[0-9]|:61[0-9]\" | head -3"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":111427,"output":188,"cacheRead":498,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":112113,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782371999253,"responseId":"068c099fb988f336ccf21e0cd3dbf531","responseModel":"MiniMax-M3"}}
