{"type":"message","id":"8c6d6c2b","parentId":"4729ab0d","timestamp":"2026-06-25T07:20:28.978Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**找到了：openclaw pid 932**。**DISPLAY 没传给那个进程。** 我直接 export 给那个进程的环境，**或者更简单：用 headless 模式启动 browser**（你看不到窗口，但能跑通）："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_3cc0er2k7eb5_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 看 gateway 进程的 env\ncat /proc/932/environ 2>/dev/null | tr '\\0' '\\n' | grep -iE \"display|wayland\" | head -5\necho \"---\"\n# 有没有办法 inject DISPLAY\ncat /proc/932/status 2>/dev/null | head -5\necho \"---\"\n# 看这个 gateway 是 s6 启的还是 systemd\nls -la /proc/932/cwd 2>/dev/null\nps -o pid,ppid,cmd -p 932 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":245,"output":190,"cacheRead":113007,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":113442,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782372023749,"responseId":"068c09b839362ae1c75c280402819765","responseModel":"MiniMax-M3"}}
