{"type":"message","id":"d5a3afcb","parentId":"7c0445b0","timestamp":"2026-06-25T07:21:13.834Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**clawpanel 不是 s6 服务**——是 OpenClaw 的 UI 工具。OpenClaw gateway 是别的方式起的。\n\n**我换种简单办法——用 openclaw gateway restart 把 DISPLAY 注入到环境：**"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_i7znxg6be538_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 看 openclaw gateway 的 service 类型\nps -o pid,ppid,sid,cmd -p 932 2>/dev/null\necho \"---\"\n# 父进程 878\nps -o pid,ppid,cmd -p 878 2>/dev/null\necho \"---\"\n# 它是不是用 pam_env 或 systemd-run 起的\ncat /proc/878/cmdline 2>/dev/null | tr '\\0' ' '\necho\ncat /proc/878/status 2>/dev/null | head -3\necho \"---\"\n# 让我看看现在 chrome 能不能在 :10 起\nDISPLAY=:10 google-chrome --version 2>&1 | head -2\necho \"---\"\nDISPLAY=:10 google-chrome --headless=new --no-sandbox --dump-dom https://www.google.com 2>&1 | head -3 | wc -l"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":51,"output":258,"cacheRead":114247,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":114556,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782372066937,"responseId":"068c09e3f354a15ce5ac5169c80527b0","responseModel":"MiniMax-M3"}}
