{"type":"message","id":"3fdc1626","parentId":"ef7e8238","timestamp":"2026-06-25T07:21:48.049Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**重大发现：openclaw gateway 是 systemd user 服务起的**（PPID 878 = `--user systemd`）。\n\n**systemd 的 user service，环境变量要写进 `~/.config/environment.d/` 或 service 文件里。** 最简单：临时给 PID 932 注 DISPLAY："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_lnspo1zn6nct_1","name":"process","arguments":{"action":"kill","sessionId":"grand-cove"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_lnspo1zn6nct_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 写个环境文件给 systemd-user\nmkdir -p /home/halei/.config/environment.d\ncat > /home/halei/.config/environment.d/10-display.conf << 'EOF'\nDISPLAY=:10\nWAYLAND_DISPLAY=wayland-0\nEOF\necho \"env file written\"\ncat /home/halei/.config/environment.d/10-display.conf\necho \"---\"\n# 重新加载 systemd user\nsystemctl --user daemon-reload\necho \"daemon-reload done\"\necho \"---\"\n# 重启 openclaw gateway service\nsystemctl --user status openclaw 2>&1 | head -3\necho \"---\"\n# 看现在能不能给 PID 932 inject env（用 prctl 不行；用 nsenter 也不行；只能重启）\n# 重启 openclaw\nsystemctl --user restart openclaw 2>&1 | head -5"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":145,"output":305,"cacheRead":114645,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":115095,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782372101951,"responseId":"068c0a062d296ca2e6ff95e6609c956a","responseModel":"MiniMax-M3"}}
