{"type":"message","id":"648e63ce","parentId":"8a5da9ed","timestamp":"2026-06-25T07:22:02.070Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**OpenClaw 是直接以 node 命令起的（不是 systemd 服务）—— 命令行是 `node ... openclaw dist/index.js gateway --port 18789`**。**DISPLAY 没在 env 里因为 systemd --user 没把环境传下去。**\n\n我有个简单办法：**用 `openclaw` 工具的 gateway restart（它自己 restart 时应该会重新读配置 / env），或者直接 kill 重启。** 或者最直接：**`/proc/932/environ` 不让外部修改，所以只能 kill 这个进程让它父进程（systemd --user）重启它：**\n\n实际上——**`openclaw` 6.x 是用 `openclaw` CLI 内部 fork 的，父进程是 systemd --user**。`systemd --user` 不知道它挂了，所以不会重启。\n\n**最稳的办法：直接 kill 932，然后用相同 env 启动新进程（带上 DISPLAY）：**"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_tyh2c7ruw7lw_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 看 932 的父 878 在不在\nkill -0 878 2>/dev/null && echo \"878 alive\" || echo \"878 dead\"\necho \"---\"\n# 看 878 是不是自动重启 932\nps -o pid,ppid,cmd --ppid 878 2>/dev/null | head -5\necho \"---\"\n# kill 932，看 systemd --user 会不会自动重启\nkill 932\nsleep 3\nps -o pid,ppid,cmd -p 932 2>/dev/null || echo \"932 dead\"\n# 看新进程\nps aux | grep \"openclaw/dist/index.js\" | grep -v grep | head -3"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":943,"output":357,"cacheRead":115304,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":116604,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782372112846,"responseId":"068c0a111bbbc6d5247b9a063b8ec750","responseModel":"MiniMax-M3"}}
